OL,3,CHospital declares critical incident
OL,4,Cover leaking roof
OL,6,FA critical incident has been declared
OL,7,Fat a leak-hit hospital after "more
OL,8,Fserious internal long-term damage" has
OL,9,Fbeen identified.
OL,11,FCwm Taf Morgannwg University Health
OL,12,FBoard released a statement on Thursday
OL,13,Fwhich said it is "exploring all
OL,14,Foptions" after a survey identified
OL,15,Fserious damage to the roof of the
OL,16,FPrincess of Wales Hospital in
OL,17,FBridgend, which will require extensive
OL,18,Frepair.
