OL,3,CHospital declares critical incident
OL,4,Cover leaking roof
OL,6,FRain water has been entering the
OL,7,Fbuilding through the roof, but
OL,8,Fauthorities now know the scale of the
OL,9,Fproblem to be much bigger than
OL,10,Fpreviously thought.
OL,12,FThe statement indicated that some of
OL,13,Fthe care being delivered at the
OL,14,FPrincess of Wales Hospital will be
OL,15,Fmoved to elsewhere within the health
OL,16,Fboard area in order to "provide care
OL,17,Fin a safe environment".
OL,19,FThose who have planned appointments at
OL,20,Fthe hospital are encouraged to attend
OL,21,Funless they are informed otherwise.
