OL,6,FThe health board said the work is
OL,7,Fbeing treated "as a priority" and a
OL,8,Fplan is currently being established.
OL,10,FThe full statement from the health
OL,11,Fboard said: "Following ongoing issues
OL,12,Fat Princess of Wales Hospital with
OL,13,Frain water entering the building
OL,14,Fthrough the roof, specialist
OL,15,Fcontractors have conducted a full
OL,16,Fsurvey of the condition of the roof of
OL,17,Fthe main building across the site.
