OL,6,F"As well as informing some immediate
OL,7,Factions, that survey has identified
OL,8,Fmore serious internal long-term damage
OL,9,Fto the roof of the hospital that will
OL,10,Frequire an extensive programme of
OL,11,Freplacement and repair.
OL,13,F"We are dealing with this as a
OL,14,Fcritical incident, and are now
OL,15,Fexploring all options to ensure we can
OL,16,Fcontinue to provide care in a safe
OL,17,Fenvironment for those patients and
OL,18,Fstaff in our wards and those who will
OL,19,Fneed care in the future.
