OL,6,F"The options will need to include the
OL,7,Fuse of the whole health board's
OL,8,Ffacilities to ensure we have the
OL,9,Fcapacity to meet all our patients'
OL,10,Fneeds.
OL,12,F"We are treating this work as a
OL,13,Fpriority and will continue to
OL,14,Fcommunicate with people directly and
OL,15,Fthrough the range of channels
OL,16,Favailable to us."
