OL,6,F"We fully appreciate how this is both
OL,7,Fconcerning and disruptive for patients
OL,8,Fand their families, but we are
OL,9,Fcommitted to putting these plans in
OL,10,Fplace to ensure our patients continue
OL,11,Fto be cared for properly and safely.
OL,13,F"This will involve some health board
OL,14,Fservices and care being provided in a
OL,15,Fdifferent place. We are currently
OL,16,Fworking through these options to
OL,17,Fensure that this causes minimal
OL,18,Fdisruption to patients.
