OL,6,F"While this is a significant
OL,7,Fsituation, moving patients is not
OL,8,Funusual ` it regularly takes place to
OL,9,Fenable patients to receive scans, or
OL,10,Freceive treatment. Our staff are very
OL,11,Fused to responding quickly to ensure
OL,12,Fcontinuity of patient care during
OL,13,Fchallenging times."
OL,15,FOther large hospitals in the health
OL,16,Fboard area are the Royal Glamorgan
OL,17,FHospital in Llantrisant and Prince
OL,18,FCharles Hospital in Merthyr Tydfil.
